name: TheVectorPack
body:
I'll use this for downloads, screenshots, and later on maybe a customizer.  If I can ever figure out how to make one.

To install, simply download the zip file and insert into your .minecraft/resourcepacks (or wherever you have your resourcepacks folder).  Switch to it ingame, and enjoy my weird vectory work!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
